<dita>
   <concept id="FAR_12_204" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">12.204</ph> Solicitation/contract
form.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d684e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
               </p>
               <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e15">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> The contracting officer shall
use the <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Standard Form 1449</xref>,
Solicitation/Contract/Order for Commercial Products and Commercial
Services, if—</p>
                     <ol class="- topic/ol ">
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e24">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>The
acquisition is expected to exceed the simplified acquisition threshold;</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e29">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>A paper
solicitation or contract is being issued; and</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="- topic/li ">
                           <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e34">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>Procedures
at <xref href="12.603.dita#FAR_12_603"
                                    base="i1112649"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">12.603</xref> are not being used.</p>
                        </li>
                     </ol>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e42">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>Use of the <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/solicitationcontractorder-commercial-items"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">SF 1449</xref> is
nonmandatory but encouraged for commercial acquisitions not exceeding
the simplified acquisition threshold.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d711e50">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Consistent
with the requirements at <xref href="5.203.dita#FAR_5_203"
                        base="i1120755"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">5.203</xref>(a)
and (h), the contracting officer may allow fewer than 15 days before issuance
of the solicitation.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
